- **Linting**: Python (`flake8`, `bandit`) + Ansible (`ansible-lint`)  
- **Deployment**: Auto-deploys to `/opt/epiq-deploy/` on target host when pushing to `main`  

CI/CD pipeline defined in `.gitlab-ci.yml`.

